name: Tusken Raider
Lore: '''Sand People.'' Ride banthas. Wield gaderffi (gaffi) sticks. Wear eye protectors and breath masks. Violent, nomadic, desert survival experts. ''Urrrg! Ur Ur Uur!''',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +1 if another non-unique Tusken Raider present. If you have four or more non-unique Tusken Raiders present, your total power here is +2.',
